OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FParts of Sherwood Forest in
OL,8,FNottinghamshire have been illegally
OL,9,Fcut down by contractors, leaving
OL,10,Flocals "angry and upset".
OL,12,FNewark and Sherwood District Council
OL,13,Fsaid contractors had felled some trees
OL,14,Fthey were not supposed to as part of a
OL,15,Flong-term project to introduce more
OL,16,Fnative species at Intake Wood.
OL,18,FThe alleged illegal felling is being
OL,19,Finvestigated by the Forestry
OL,20,FCommission.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FCarl Atkin, who has lived in the area
OL,8,Ffor 17 years said:
OL,10,F"I'm absolutely stunned. If I had done
OL,11,Fthat as a resident I'd be quite
OL,12,Frightly held accountable for that".
OL,14,F"I'm angry and upset because
OL,15,Fultimately they've done work they
OL,16,Fshouldn't have. They're completely
OL,17,Fdevastating the landscape.
OL,19,F"The contractors chopped down trees
OL,20,Fillegally and they've been allowed
OL,21,Ffour days later to carry on working."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FCouncillor Paul Peacock, the Leader of
OL,8,FNewark and Sherwood District Council,
OL,9,Fsaid the authority was investigating
OL,10,Fthe accidental felling of a section of
OL,11,Ftrees situated towards the western
OL,12,Fedge of the woodland.
OL,14,FHe said: "We are aware that a section
OL,15,Fof woodland has been felled when it
OL,16,Fwas not supposed to be. This was not
OL,17,Fpart of the plan, and we are
OL,18,Finvestigating what has happened".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,F"We are committed to doing everything
OL,8,Fpossible, working with the Forestry
OL,9,FCommission, to identify why this
OL,10,Foccurred, and take action to put
OL,11,Fthings right.
OL,13,F"We will continue to work with the
OL,14,Flocal community to provide updates on
OL,15,Four investigation."
OL,17,FPreviously, Cllr Peacock had said the
OL,18,Fongoing work was important to ensure
OL,19,Fthe woodland was "protected for
OL,20,Fgenerations to come".
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FHe said the area was transitioning
OL,8,Ffrom non-native Corsican Pine trees,
OL,9,Fwhich are grown for timber, to
OL,10,Fbroadleaf woodland, which usually
OL,11,Fconsists of deciduous trees such as
OL,12,Foak, ash, beech and birch.
OL,14,FAlthough the contracted work is
OL,15,Fexpected to end by May, the thinning
OL,16,Fof some pine trees had increased the
OL,17,Frisk of the remaining trees falling
OL,18,Fonto nearby houses.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FCllr Peacock said contractors were
OL,8,Fchecking each tree for nests before
OL,9,Fchopping it down and had held
OL,10,Fdiscussions with officers from the
OL,11,FForestry Commission and other
OL,12,Fenvironmental professionals.
OL,14,FBut locals living nearby say they've
OL,15,Fbeen left shocked by the speed and
OL,16,Fscale of the work, claiming it had
OL,17,Fleft some paths in a "treacherous"
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776780668
OL,3,CLocals 'angry and upset' after parts
OL,4,Cof Sherwood Forest illegally chopped
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FThey also raised questions over the
OL,8,Ftiming of the work, which coincides
OL,9,Fwith bird nesting season.
OL,11,FThe Forestry Commission have been
OL,12,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
